===Etymology===
From {{etyl|hi|en}} {{m|hi|मध्य प्रदेश}} (madhya pradeś) "middle province", from {{etyl|sa|en}} {{m|sa|मध्य}} (madhya) "middle, central",  {{m|sa|प्रदेश}} (pradeśa) "region, country".
